    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "Application Features\n\nHome Screen\n    Provides users with a simple
    and intuitive interface to start the AR learning experience.\n\nAR Plane Detection\n   
    Uses AR Foundation and ARCore to detect flat real-world surfaces where anatomical
    models can be placed.\n\nHeart Model Placement\n   Allows users to place a 3D
    human heart model into their physical environment through touch interaction.\n\nInteractive
    Anatomical Hotspots\n   Users can tap different regions of the heart to explore
    anatomical structures.\n\nEducational Information Panel\n   Displays the name
    and description of selected heart structures, providing an interactive learning
    experience.\n\n"
